description.en:
The DIM (Data Interchange Module) is an alternative coin (altcoin) that is available in multiple variations: DIMCOIN, DIM Currencies and DIM Cryptocurrencies. DIMCOIN is a speculative coin that is traded against other cryptocurrencies on exchanges according to market forces. DIM Currencies are stable means of exchange in the DIM Ecosystem (DIM-E), and they are supported by precious metals and highly liquid cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin. The DIM Cryptocurrencies are DIM denominated mosaics of popular cryptocurrencies, for example, Bitcoin (BTC) can be converted into DIM BTC in order to be used in the DIM Ecosystem. DIMCOIN offered the first entry into the ecosystem which offers services such as; cryptonization, cryptonized-equities (blockshares), cryptonized-equity exchange trading, cryptocurrency exchange, e-commerce, inter-business (B2B) transactions and further blockchain business solutions.

DIM and its Ecosystem operate independently from the DIM Foundation. They were originally funded through ICO crowd-funding which awarded participants with DIM TOKENs. These DIM TOKENs offer holders the right to make suggestions and to vote on the direction of the ecosystem. DIM is based on NEM's blockchain technology, meaning DIM offers a unique multi-tier design using node reputation, spam protection, and incentivised infrastructure to ensure safe and secure online transactions. DIMCOIN and other offerings in the DIM-E can be managed on these online wallets, such as DEPOTWALLET, DIMWALLET and DIMPAY. DIM X is a platform that exchanges different cryptocurrencies into Data Interchange Modules. The Hybrid Stock Exchange (HYBSE) is the online market place for global issuers and users that provides a wide range of tradable cryptonized equities.

DIM Currencies are stable means of exchange in the DIM Ecosystem (DIM-E), and they are supported by precious metals and highly liquid cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin. The DIM Cryptocurrencies are DIM denominated mosaics of popular cryptocurrencies, for example, Bitcoin (BTC) can be converted into DIM BTC in order to be used in the DIM Ecosystem. DIMCOIN offered the first entry into the ecosystem which offers services such as; cryptonization, cryptonized-equities (blockshares), cryptonized-equity exchange trading, cryptocurrency exchange, e-commerce, inter-business (B2B) transactions and further blockchain business solutions.

DIM and its Ecosystem operate independently from the DIM Foundation. They were originally funded through ICO crowd-funding which awarded participants with DIM TOKENs. These DIM TOKENs offer holders the right to make suggestions and to vote on the direction of the ecosystem. DIM is based on NEM's blockchain technology, meaning DIM offers a unique multi-tier design using node reputation, spam protection, and incentivised infrastructure to ensure safe and secure online transactions. DIMCOIN and other offerings in the DIM-E can be managed on these online wallets, such as DEPOTWALLET, DIMWALLET and DIMPAY. DIM X is a platform that exchanges different cryptocurrencies into Data Interchange Modules. The Hybrid Stock Exchange (HYBSE) is the online market place for global issuers and users that provides a wide range of tradable cryptonized equities.

ico_data.short_desc: The Future of Equity on the Blockchain
ico_data.description: DIM (Data Interchange Module) is a cryptocurrency based on NEM technology. The DIM has two versions: DIMCOIN - a speculative and tradable cryptocurrency & DIM Currencies: a means of exchange within the DIM Ecosystem. The DIM Ecosystem is a community of complementary blockchain-based virtual currencies and transactional services. The services include: cryptonisation (virtualisation) of equity, trading in cryptonised shares and assets, cryptocurrency exchanges, crypto-fiat currency exchanges, e-commerce, debit card purchases, business transactions and commodity trading and other cryptonised instruments.
ico_data.accepting_currencies: BTC, ETH, LTC, XEM, DASH, USDT
